00px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>伦敦 E1 夜总会创始人因前往加沙为以色列国防军 (IDF) 服役而辞职。</p><p>据<a href="https://mixmag.net/read/e1-owner-resigns-idf-gaza-israel-palestine-news" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>Mixmag</i></a>报道，这一消息是由 Ravers For Palestine 组织标记的，该组织分享了一张现已删除的 Facebook 帖子的屏幕截图，其中显示 Yuval Hen 穿着以色列国防军制服，并配文称他在入狱四个月后将“返回家园”。加沙。</p><p> E1 在一份声明中表示，这是“一个音乐和舞蹈的场所”，并且“与政治运动无关，并确认我们的前任所有者因深受以色列和巴勒斯坦持续危机的影响而于 10 月辞职” ”。</p><p>声明继续说道：“我们将继续为人们在东伦敦享受俱乐部文化提供一个安全的空间。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C3YThMbMEDf/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.